sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Kueue Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Controller as Kueue Controller Manager
    participant CQ as ClusterQueue
    participant Workload as Workload CRD
    participant Job as Kubernetes Job
    participant Autoscaler as cluster-autoscaler

    Note over User,Autoscaler: Flow 1: Job Submission and Queueing

    User->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/batch/v1/namespaces/{ns}/jobs<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-batch-v1-job<br/>mTLS (API Server identity)
    Webhook->>Webhook: Inject Kueue labels<br/>Set suspend=true
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Modified Job spec
    K8sAPI-->>User: Job created (suspended)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: WATCH /apis/batch/v1/jobs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Controller: Detect new Job
    Controller->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/workloads<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over Controller,Workload: Create Workload resource for Job

    Note over User,Autoscaler: Flow 2: Workload Admission

    Controller->>K8sAPI: WATCH /apis/kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/clusterqueues<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Controller: Check resource quotas<br/>Evaluate priorities and queueing policy
    Controller->>CQ: Check available quota<br/>Apply StrictFIFO/BestEffortFIFO
    CQ-->>Controller: Quota available

    Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH /apis/kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/workloads/{name}<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over Controller,Workload: Admit Workload (assign quota)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH /apis/batch/v1/jobs/{name}<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over Controller,Job: Set suspend=false (unsuspend Job)

    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-batch-v1-job<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation passed

    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Job updated
    K8sAPI->>Job: Schedule pods

    Note over User,Autoscaler: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics (8080/TCP)<br/>HTTP plaintext
    Controller-->>Prometheus: kueue_pending_workloads<br/>kueue_admitted_workloads_total<br/>kueue_cluster_queue_resource_usage

    Note over User,Autoscaler: Flow 4: Provisioning Request (Autoscaling)

    Controller->>Controller: Detect insufficient resources<br/>for pending Workload
    Controller->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/autoscaling.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/provisioningrequests<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over Controller,Autoscaler: Request node provisioning

    Autoscaler->>K8sAPI: WATCH /apis/autoscaling.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/provisioningrequests<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Autoscaler->>Autoscaler: Provision new nodes
    Autoscaler->>K8sAPI: PATCH /apis/autoscaling.x-k8s.io/v1beta1/provisioningrequests/{name}<br/>Update status

    Controller->>K8sAPI: WATCH ProvisioningRequest status<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Controller: Retry admission when nodes ready
